  in his or her lifetime and have witnesses to it. In these times\, the Will
  has become extremely important. Muslims may find that a sharia compliant w
 ill ensure your wishes are carried \nout in accordance with your faith\, so
 mething that may be omitted by a typical U.S. will writing service. We prov
 ide Islamic Will writing service to Muslims who wish to leave their estates
  in accordance with Islamic law. carefully written to ensure that in the ev
 ent of your passing\, your estate and wealth are distributed in accordance 
 with Islamic law\, whilst also complying with what is required by US Federa
 l and State law.
